2008-11-27  Jerome Galtier  <jerome.galtier@lrde.epita.fr>

	XML: Overhaul support for series representations.
	* data/vaucanson.xsd: New complexType `seriesWritingData'. Rework
	  the `writingData' element in `valueType'.
