	  patches.

2008-11-08  Jerome Galtier  <jerome.galtier@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix the is_ltl algorithm.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/is_ltl.hxx (do_is_ltl): Remove the
	  `CHECK_LTL_CONDITION' macro. Change the check performed on initial
	  and final transitions.
	* src/tests/include/tests/automata/algos/fmp_transducers/is_ltl_test.hh:
	  Update the test to correspond to the fixed ltl semantic.

