	  literal_to_letter return a std::pair<bool, letter_t> to handle
	  parsing errors and fix functions that use it.
	* include/vaucanson/algebra/implementation/letter/char_letter.hh,
	* include/vaucanson/algebra/implementation/letter/char_letter.hxx,
	* include/vaucanson/algebra/implementation/letter/couple_letter.hh,
