2008-11-01  Alexandre Duret-Lutz  <adl@lrde.epita.fr>

	Get rid of dump-automaton. The command "dump-automaton file.xml"
	can now be replaced by "identity file.xml" if there is no
	"file.xml" in the current directory.

	* taf-kit/src/library_commands.hh (dump_automaton_command): Remove.
	* taf-kit/src/common_commands.hh (USE_IO_COMMAND_GROUP): Remove dump.
	* taf-kit/tests/vcsn-char-b.test: Adjust.

