	from VCSN_DATA_PATH if it is not in the current directory.

2008-11-01  Alexandre Duret-Lutz  <adl@lrde.epita.fr>

	Change get_aut() and get_exp() to take arguments_t as first
	argument.  For get_exp() this is a simplification, for
	get_aut() this prepares the following patch.

	* taf-kit/src/getters.hh (get_exp): Remove.
	(get_exp_complete): Rename as get_exp() and use two arguments.
	(get_aut): Use two arguments.
	* taf-kit/src/getters.hxx (get_exp, get_aut): Adjust.
