	DEFINE_ONE_ARG_COMMAND_TWO_ALGOS_, DEFINE_TWO_ARGS_COMMAND_,
	DEFINE_IS_PROPERTY_COMMAND): Adjust to call get_aut() and
	get_exp() using two arguments.
	* taf-kit/src/common_automaton_commands.hh,
	taf-kit/src/common_commands.hh, taf-kit/src/fmp_commands.cc,
	taf-kit/src/ratexp_commands.hh, taf-kit/src/b_commands.cc:
	Adjust all calls to get_aut() or get_exp().

