2008-11-03  Jerome Galtier  <jerome.galtier@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix a bug in Taf-Kit's print_automaton.
	* taf-kit/src/edition_commands.hxx (print_automaton): Use
	  `series_of' instead of `series_value_of'.

2008-11-03  Jerome Galtier  <jerome.galtier@lrde.epita.fr>

	Refactor token_representation_t.
	* taf-kit/src/common.hh,
	* taf-kit/src/edition_commands.hxx,
