2008-10-24  Reuben Thomas  <rrt@sc3d.org>

	Fix English.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/realtime.hh: Fix English.

2008-10-23  Alexandre Duret-Lutz  <adl@lrde.epita.fr>

	* configure.ac: Add -DBOOST_MULTI_INDEX_DISABLE_SERIALIZATION to
	BOOST_CPPFLAGS, so that boost::multi_index does not include
	boost::serialize.  We do not need serialize, it works around
	problems when people do not have the package installed, and it
	is less work for the preprocessor.  (This fixes ticket #184)

