	Fix a bug in the is_sub_normalized algorithm.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/sub_normalize.hxx
	  (so_is_sub_normalized): When iterating over the final transitions,
	  use `get_final' instead of `get_initial' to retrieve the label.
