2008-10-13  Jerome Galtier  <jerome.galtier@lrde.epita.fr>

	Overhaul the is_letterized_transducer algorithm.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/is_letterized.hh: Improve
	  the documentation. Update the copyright notice. Cosmetic changes.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/is_letterized.hxx: Add the required
	  `freemonoid_product.hh' header. Reorder headers.
	  (do_is_letterized_transducer): Add one argument to check for the
	  monoid type. Add corresponding templates arguments `A' and `B'. Rename
	  template argument `A' to `T'. Rewrite the algorithm
	  implementation: it made wrong assumptions about the properties of
	  an FMP transducer. Cosmetic changes.
	  (is_letterized_transducer): Move TIMER_SCOPED macro to
	  `do_is_letterized_transducer'. Use `monoid()' to extract type
	  information of the automaton argument.

