2008-10-03  Reuben Thomas  <rrt@sc3d.org>

	Add config.h.in to svn:ignore properties.

2008-10-03  Reuben Thomas  <rrt@sc3d.org>

	Remove use of AX_BOOST_WSERIALIZATION.
	* build-aux/ax_boost_wserialization.m4: Remove.
	* configure.ac: Don't use AX_BOOST_WSERIALIZATION, as it
	  doesn't really do what we want: it detects the binary
	  library as well as the headers, but we don't need that,
	  as we only use the headers. There's no macro that does
	  what we want, so just note the fact in configure.ac.

