2008-09-30  Reuben Thomas  <rrt@sc3d.org>

	Add .libs to svn:ignore.

2008-09-30    <rrt@sc3d.org>

	Add some svn:ignore patterns.

2008-09-29  Jerome Galtier  <jerome.galtier@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix bad practice in header files.
	* include/vaucanson/algebra/implementation/letter/couple_letter.hh:
	  Move implementation to...
