2008-05-28  Jimmy Ma  <jimmy.ma@lrde.epita.fr>

	Add new delta iterators.
	They provide new iterating features that does not imply the
	copying of data.

	* bmig/iterator.hh,
	  bmig/iterator.hxx: The implementation of deltai on bmig.

	* bmig_graph_impl.hh,
	  bmig_graph_impl.hxx:
	  Add the types that will be used by the users.
	  Add helpers for the implementation of delta iterators:
	    - deltai give a range of iterators on a subindex of the hash
	      table.
	    - get_htransition give a htransition_t corresponding to an
	      iterator on a subindex of the hash table.

	* listg/iterator.hh,
	  listg/iterator.hxx: The implementation of deltai on listg.

	* listg_graph_impl.hh: Add the types that will be used by the users.

	* transpose_view.hh: Add the missing types to the automaton_trait.

