2008-03-21  Alexandre Duret-Lutz  <adl@lrde.epita.fr>

	We should not run "make check" in taf-kit if the taf-kit binaries
	have been disabled.

	* Makefile.am (SUBDIRS): Rewrite using the MAYBE_ idiom.  Recurse
	into taf-kit conditionally.
	* taf-kit/src/Makefile.am (bin_PROGRAMS): Build all programs
	unconditionally.
	* build-aux/vcsn-taf-kit.m4 (VCSN_TAF_KIT): Rename as ...
	(ENABLE_TAF_KIT): ... for consistency.

2008-03-21  Alexandre Duret-Lutz  <adl@lrde.epita.fr>

