	flags passed to configure during distcheck.

	* configure.ac (MORE_DISTCHECK_CONFIGURE_FLAGS): Populate this
	variable with the --with-python, --with-boost, and --with-xerces
	flags that were passed to configure.
	* Makefile.am (DISTCHECK_CONFIGURE_FLAGS): Use
	MORE_DISTCHECK_CONFIGURE_FLAGS.

