	  Disable the xml diffs because the cannot be accurate because
	  of the state renumbering done with bmig.

2008-03-18  Jimmy Ma  <jimmy.ma@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix is_ambiguous.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/is_ambiguous.hxx:
	  We need to create a map of correspondance to work with the set
	  filled by product. This is related to the copy of the automaton
	  and the fact that hstates are dependant of the automaton.

