2008-03-16  Jimmy Ma  <jimmy.ma@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix algorithm sub_automaton().
	* sub_automaton.hxx:
	  Fix errors related to automata copy.
	  Create a new hstate_t set containing the hstates corresponding
	  to the new automaton.

2008-03-16  Jimmy Ma  <jimmy.ma@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix rw_composition.
	* internal/evaluation.hxx,
	* rw_composition.hxx:
	  Correct errors related to state renumbering and automata copy.
	  hstates_t are linked to an automaton and should not be used on
	  an other one. To do this, we must either convert them back to
	  integer when possible and ask for the corresponding state, or
	  use a map to link states from one automaton to the other.

2008-03-16  Jimmy Ma  <jimmy.ma@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix hstate_t related bugs: operators and has_state().
	* bmig/bmig_handlers_op.hxx:
	  Fix hstate_t operators: we now compare the address of the int
	  instead of its value. It allows correct use of sets or maps
	  in combination with state renumbering.

	* bmig_graph_impl.hxx:
	  Correction of the has_state method.

