	* src/tests/include/Makefile.am: .
	* src/tests/include/tests/automata/algos/letter_combination_labeled_graphs/transition_container_test.hh: New.
	Miswritten operators were the source of this bug.
	This test contains basic tests on operator<, and basic insertions
	on std::list, multiset and set.

