	* include/vaucanson/automata/implementation/boostg_graph_impl.hxx:
	remove structure declarations made in the Graph object and update the
	typedefs.
	* include/vaucanson/automata/implementation/legacy/legacy_sparse_interval.hh:
	add a missing namespace information.

