2008-03-04  Florian Lesaint  <florian.lesaint@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fixe script incompatibilities with Mac.
	* include/generate_headers.sh: Remove use of -printf with find,
	    since this option doesn't exist on BSD find.
	    Use -exec combined with basename instead.
	* src/tests/sanity/generate_files.sh: Remove use of 	 in sed,
	    since the conversion doesn't work on BSD sed.
	    Use a real tabulation instead.

