2007-12-13  Alexandre Duret-Lutz  <adl@lrde.epita.fr>

	Taf-Kit's tests suite failed to notice several mistakes because
	"set -e" has no effects on commands prefixed by "!"...  Besides,
	"!" does not make any difference between an expected error code
	and a segfault.

	* tests/defs.in (fail1): New function.
	(non_ambiguous1): Really point to a non-ambiguous automaton.
	* tests/vcsn-b.test: Use fail1 instead of !.  Fix test for
	is-realtime.
	* tests/vcsn-z.test: Use fail1 instead of !.  Do not test for
	is-normalized, it does not exist, and fix the tests for
	is-ambiguous and is-realtime.
	* tests/vcsn-tdc.test: Use fail1 instead of !.  Really disable
	the test for are-isomorphic.

2007-12-05  Alexandre Duret-Lutz  <adl@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fixes for files left in build directory after distclean.

	* taf-kit/tests/defs.in: Fix the creation of working directories.
	* data/Makefile.am (dist_lisp_LISP): Do not list emacs/* files here
	because Automake fails to clean lisp files in subdirectories. Do it...
	* data/emacs/Makefile.am: ... in this new file.
	* data/Makefile.am (SUBDIRS): Recurse into emacs.
	* configure.ac: Output data/emacs/Makefile.
	* doc/Makefile.am: Do not include doc.mk, its intricate set of
	circular pattern rules cause the PDF files to be rebuilt in VPATH
	builds, breaking distcheck.
	* src/tests/test-suites/test-suite.mk (CLEANFILES): Clean
	coherence_state_transition_test.xml because it is output by many
	test suite.  Move the rest of that variable ...
	* src/tests/check/check.mk (CLEANFILES): ... here, so that
	handwritten test-suites get cleaned too.

2007-12-04  Alexandre Duret-Lutz  <adl@lrde.epita.fr>

	Revert the change of 2007-10-22.  It breaks "make distcheck" and
	fails to install files that are essential to taf-kit.

	* Makefile.am (SUBDIRS): Add data.
	(demos): Do not recurse into data.

