2007-12-03  Alexandre Duret-Lutz  <adl@lrde.epita.fr>

	Introduce are_equivalent, and use it to fix a failure in the
	test-suite.

	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/equivalent.hh,
	include/vaucanson/algorithms/equivalent.hxx: New files.
	* include/Makefile.am: Distribute and install them.
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/automaton_functions.thh: Include them.
	* lib/generate_libvcsn.rb: Add are_equivalent.
	* taf-kit/src/b_commands.cc: Add the are-equivalent command.
	* taf-kit/tests/vcsn-b.test: Add a test for are-equivalent.
	* src/tests/include/tests/automata/algos/fmp_transducers/normalized_composition_test.hh,
	src/tests/include/tests/automata/algos/fmp_transducers/evaluation_fmp_test.hh,
	src/tests/include/tests/automata/algos/fmp_transducers/subnormalized_composition_test.hh:
