	are equivalent, not by comparing their syntax trees.  This fixes a
	failure of normalized_composition-test.
	* src/tests/include/tests/automata/algos/boolean_rw_transducers/invert_test.hh:
	Remove the kludge I introduced on 2007-11-02 and an older one.

