2007-10-29  Guillaume Leroi  <guillaume.leroi@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix final transitions handling in standardize.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/standard.hxx: Accumulate final
	transitions series and add the result to the new initial state.
	Suppress only non-accessible initial states, not all
	non-accessible states.
	* taf-kit/tests/vcsn-b.test: Add a test on standardize. Check
	that final transitions are handle.

2007-10-23  Guillaume Leroi  <guillaume.leroi@lrde.epita.fr>

