	Commands taking two parameters were outputing nothing.
	This was due to change in macros since internal pipe was add.

	* taf-kit/src/commands_macros.hh: Use KEEP_AUTOMATON instead of OUTPUT.
	* taf-kit/tests/vcsn-b.test: Add tests on two paramater	commands to
	check that they ouput some XML.

