2007-10-11  Guillaume Lazzara  <z@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix make distcheck
	The vaucanswig's Makefiles were not generated properly.
	Morover, the make distcheck now use two configure options:
	--enable-demos and --enable-vaucanswig.

	* Makefile.am: Fix the distcheck options.
	* configure.ac: Fix the vaucanswig's makefiles generation.

2007-10-10  Guillaume Leroi  <guillaume.leroi@lrde.epita.fr>

	Remove contains_factors demo.
	The algortihm is false, and failed to check if the language
	recognized by an automaton is factor of a language recognized
	by an other automaton.
	* src/demos/algorithms/Makefile.am: Remove target {b,z}_contains_factor.
	* src/demos/algorithms/contains_factor.cc: Remove.

2007-10-10  Guillaume Leroi  <guillaume.leroi@lrde.epita.fr>

	Rename predefined alphabets
	`ascii' has been suppress too, because the xml parser cannot handle `"',
	and Vaucanson does not handle correctly alphabets with digits.
	* taf-kit/src/main.cc: Rename `a-z' to letters and `a-zA-Z' to alpha.

