2007-10-02  Guillaume Lazzara  <z@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix the PYTHON_PREFIX detection.
	Add a new test to override the default python prefix.
	The python prefix was set to PREFIX by default. However,
	you may want to change it and it is usually installed in
	a different path than PREFIX.

	* configure.ac: add the test.

2007-10-02  Guillaume Lazzara  <z@lrde.epita.fr>

	Make the doc generation optional.
	You need to type 'make docs' to generate the docs.
	Avoid dependencies issues when the user doesn't have
	doxygen installed.

	* Makefile.am,
	* doc/Makefile.am: Add a docs rule.

