2007-09-20  Guillaume Lazzara  <z@lrde.epita.fr>

	Disable are_isomorphic in TAF-Kit
	Since the meaning of "isomorphic" is not correctly defined in
	Vaucanson yet, this algorithm is temporarily disabled in TAF-Kit.
	It remains accesible through the usual headers if necessary.

	* taf-kit/src/tdc_commands.cc,
	* taf-kit/src/z_commands.cc: Disable are_isomorphic.

