	* taf-kit/src/pipe.hxx: New.
	* taf-kit/src/pipe_command_sequence.hh: New.
	* taf-kit/src/pipe_command_sequence.hxx: New.
	* taf-kit/src/pipe_getters.hh: New.
	* taf-kit/src/pipe_getters.hxx: New.
	* taf-kit/src/pipe_writers.hh: New.
