2007-03-29  Guillaume Leroi  <guillaume.leroi@lrde.epita.fr>

	Correct thompson algorithm behaviour on '0'.
	The Thompson's automton generated by '0' should have two states, one
	initial, one final and no transitions.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/thompson.hxx: Correct the zero method of
	ThompsonVisitor.
	* src/tests/include/tests/automata/algos/labeled_graphs/thompson_test.hh:
	Check that the automaton generated by 0 has two states and zero
	transitions.

