	Split fsm_dump.{hh,hxx} according to the documentation.
	* ../../../doc/manual/developer.tex: .
      	* fsm_load.hh: New, extracted from...
	* fsm_dump.hh: ... here.
	* fsm_load.hxx: New, extracted from...
	* fsm_dump.hxx: ... here.

