	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/product.hxx: Change reference type to
	type for attribute semiring_zero_.

	Fix a wrong ifndef condition.

2007-03-07  Guillaume Lazzara  <z@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix a wrong ifndef condition
	* composition_cover.hh: .
	* internal/build_pattern.hh: .
	* internal/partial_rat_exp.hh: .
	* internal/partial_rat_exp_constant_term.hh: .
	* internal/partial_rat_exp_derivation.hh: .

	While building the test suite, these two files could
	lead to a compiling error.


2007-03-06  Guillaume Lazzara  <z@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix includes issues
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/aut_to_exp.hxx: A header was missing.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/product.hxx: Few structures were
	only declared and implemented in this file. The structure's
	declarations have been moved to the .hh and now we keep the
	implementations only.

	Many functions like make_automaton were declared in
	contexts/*_functions.thh.
	They are now declared in new files: *_maker.t{hh,hxx}.
	These new files are included in the *_structures.hh.

	This patch will be useful for libvcsn-*.
	We may be able to instantiate the make_automaton functions
	in a .cc file to speed up the compilation.

2007-03-06  Guillaume Lazzara  <z@lrde.epita.fr>

	Include the make_automaton functions in the structures' headers.
	* include/Makefile.am: Add the new files in the list.
	* include/vaucanson/boolean_automaton_structures.hh: Add a new
	include.
	* include/vaucanson/boolean_transducer_structures.hh: Add a new
	include.
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/automaton_functions.thh: Remove
	make_automaton declaration.
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/automaton_functions.thxx: Remove, move
	its content in automaton_maker.thxx
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/automaton_maker.thh: New, contains the
	make_automaton declaration
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/automaton_maker.thxx: New, contains the
	make_automaton implementation.
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/fmp_transducer_functions.thh: Add a new
	include.
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/fmp_transducer_functions.thxx: Remove,
	move its content in fmp_transducer_maker.thxx.
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/fmp_transducer_maker.thh: New, contains
	the make_automaton declaration.
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/fmp_transducer_maker.thxx: New, contains
	the make_automaton implementation.
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/transducer_functions.thh: Add a new
	include.
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/transducer_functions.thxx: Remove, move
	its content to transducer_maker.thxx
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/transducer_maker.thh: New, contains the
	make_automaton declaration.
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/transducer_maker.thxx: New, contains the
	make_automaton implementation.
	* include/vaucanson/fmp_transducer_structures.hh: Add a new include.
	* include/vaucanson/r_automaton_structures.hh: Add a new include.
	* include/vaucanson/z_automaton_structures.hh: Add a new include.
	* include/vaucanson/z_fmp_transducer.hh: Add a new include.
	* include/vaucanson/z_fmp_transducer_structures.hh: Add anew include.
	* include/vaucanson/z_transducer_structures.hh: Add a new include.

	This patch is the continuation of the patch #1573.
	These files were forgotten in the patch #1573.

2007-03-06  Guillaume Lazzara  <z@lrde.epita.fr>

	Add forgotten VCSN_USE_LIB ifndef
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/composition_cover.hh: .
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/internal/build_pattern.hh: .
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/internal/partial_rat_exp.hh: .
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/internal/partial_rat_exp_constant_term.hh: .
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/internal/partial_rat_exp_derivation.hh: .
	* include/vaucanson/tools/dot_dump.hh: .
	* include/vaucanson/tools/dot_format.hh: .
	* include/vaucanson/tools/gen_book.hh: .
	* include/vaucanson/tools/io.hh: .
	* include/vaucanson/tools/simple_dump.hh: .
	* include/vaucanson/tools/simple_format.hh: .
	* include/vaucanson/tools/usual_io.hh: .

        This patch restores the VCSN_USE_INTERFACE_ONLY condition in the
        .hxx files (revert the patch #1561).
        A new define, VCSN_USE_LIB, has been created to explicitly not
        include the .hxx files for the algorithms (may be extended to
	other types of functions later). It will be useful whenever one will
	want to compile a binary and link it against libvcsn-*.
	It also removes the old VCSN_WITHOUT_ALGORITHMS_INCLUDES defines.

	VCSN_USE_LIB replaces VCSN_WITHOUT_ALGORITHMS_INCLUDES.

	The documentation will come in a next patch.

