2007-02-23  Guillaume Lazzara  <z@lrde.epita.fr>

	Remove useless ifndef
	Remove the ifndef related to VCSN_USE_INTERFACE_ONLY in files declaring
	automata structures.
	Indeed, most of the automata structures can't be explicitly
	instantiated and can't be part of libvcsn-*. Thus, while building
	an application linked against libvcsn, we always want to include
	.hxx files for these structures.
	* algebra/concept/alphabets_base.hh: .
	* algebra/concept/freemonoid_base.hh: .
	* algebra/concept/freemonoid_product.hh: .
	* algebra/concept/freemonoid_product_base.hh: .
	* algebra/concept/monoid_base.hh: .
	* algebra/concept/numerical_semiring.hh: .
	* algebra/concept/semigroup_base.hh: .
	* algebra/concept/semiring_base.hh: .
	* algebra/concept/series_base.hh: .
	* algebra/concept/tropical_semiring.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/alphabets/decorated_alphabet.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/alphabets/set_alphabet.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/free_monoid/str_words.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/free_monoid/tools.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/free_monoid/words.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/free_monoid_product/freemonoid_product_pair_str.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/letter/couple_letter.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/letter/int_letter.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/letter/range.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/semiring/numerical_semiring.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/semiring/rational_number.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/semiring/tropical_semiring.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/series/generalized.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/series/krat.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/series/krat_coefficient.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/series/krat_conversion.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/series/krat_exp_parser.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/series/krat_exp_pattern.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/series/polynoms.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/series/rat/depth_visitor.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/series/rat/dispatch_visitor.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/series/rat/dump_visitor.hh: .
	* algebra/implementation/series/rat/exp.hh: .
