	Prepare timer.hh for sanity checks.
	* include/vaucanson/misc/timer.hh (VAUCANSON): Define it.
	If we don't define it, then timer.cc and bencher.cc should
	be compiled and linked in, which is not the case.  This is
	what other projects want, but not Vcn.

