2007-02-03  Guillaume Leroi  <guillaume.leroi@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix final transitions handling in concat_of_standard.
	* ChangeLog: Correct some typo.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/standard.hxx: Here. Set states to
	final at the end of the algorithm.
	Backward closure was generating false transitions.
	Add some final points to comments.

2007-02-02  Guillaume Leroi  <guillaume.leroi@lrde.epita.fr>

	Correct star_of_standard.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/standard.hxx: Set weight on transitions
	added between final states and the initial one.

2007-02-02  Guillaume Leroi  <guillaume.leroi@lrde.epita.fr>

	Reorganize and correct concat_of_standard. Weight of final
	transitions where not set.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/standard.hxx: Do it. Set correctly weigth
	of final transitions of the resulting automaton.

2007-02-02  Guillaume Leroi  <guillaume.leroi@lrde.epita.fr>

	Remove dead code in union_of_standard
	* algorithms/standard.hxx: Do it. Remove operations on ingoing
	transitions of initial state.

2007-02-02  Akim Demaille  <akim@lrde.epita.fr>

	Add missing inlines.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/isomorph.hxx (Trie): here.

2007-02-02  Akim Demaille  <akim@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix are-isomorphic iterator handling.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/isomorph.hxx (Trie::L_is_valid): New.
	(Trie::Trie): New copy ctor.
	(are_isomorphic): Shorten scopes.
	Fix the definition of T_L_A and T_L_B.

2007-02-02  Akim Demaille  <akim@lrde.epita.fr>

	Shorten scopes, avoid new.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/isomorph.hxx: Let the tries be
	objects, not pointers.
	Shorten the scope for T_aux.

2007-02-02  Akim Demaille  <akim@lrde.epita.fr>

	Cleansing.
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/isomorph.hh,
