2006-10-18  Robert Bigaignon  <robert.bigaignon@lrde.epita.fr>

	Clean projections and fmp_projections, Part 1.
	Image is now available for both transducers and RW
	transducers, and is called via the overloaded algorithm
	vcsn::image ().

	vcsn::identity () is now located in projections.h{h,xx}.


	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/image.hh,
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/image.hxx: New. Implementation
	  of image for both types of transducers.

	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/projections_fmp.hh
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/projections_fmp.hxx: Remove
	  implementation of image from this file.

	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/projection.hxx
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/projection.hh: Remove
	  implementation of output_projection. Move vcsn::identity ()
	  here.


	* include/vaucanson/automata/concept/transducer.hh: Adapt
	  output projection trait.

	* include/Makefile.am,
	* include/vaucanson/contexts/fmp_transducer_functions.thh,
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/evaluation_fmp.hxx,
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/evaluation.hxx: Update
	  accordingly to use vcsn::image ().

