2006-08-30  Akim Demaille  <akim@lrde.epita.fr>

	XML cleanups.

	There are several naughty problems with our XML scheme.
	In particular, it does not encode non ASCII characters properly.
	We should use the Writers provided by Xerces instead of doing
	this ourselves.
	* include/vaucanson/xml/xml_chooser.hh: Doxygen.
	* include/vaucanson/xml/xml_chooser.hxx:
	Remove useless parens.
	(create_element, has_attribute, get_attribute): New.
	Use them.

