	Improve the usability of the generated test-suite.

	But really, it's a mess.
	To make it easier to track, stop using relative paths in the test
	suite, so move them all to another header hierarchy starting with
	"tests/".
	Adjust the generation of the test suite.
	Save cycle by avoid re-generating files that did not change.
	Cannot make a proper ChangeLog entry for all the small changes
	that were needed.
	More files should probably go into include/tests.
	* build-aux/move-if-change: Send messages to stderr.

	* configure.ac: Adjust.
	* src/tests/Makefile.am: Adjust.

