2006-07-21  Akim Demaille  <akim@lrde.epita.fr>

	Improve the TAF-Kit test suite framework.

	* include/vaucanson/xml/xerces_parser.hxx (get_xsd_path): Don't
	forget to look for the xsd file.
	* taf-kit/tests/check.mk: Improve the layout by splitting long
	string assignments.
	* taf-kit/tests/wrapper.in: New.
	* taf-kit/tests/defs.in: Use it.
	Set the PATH to use the wrappers.
	No longer use VERBOSE in anyway.
	Use a common base test directory containing sub dirs.
	* taf-kit/tests/vcsn-b.test,
	* taf-kit/tests/vcsn-z.test: No longer rely on envvars to find the
	programs to test, but only the PATH.
	* taf-kit/tests/Makefile.am: Adjust.
	* configure.ac: Fix the expansion of VCSN_DATA_PATH.
	(VCSN_ARG_PROGS): Improve the interface.
	As a consequence RST2TEX is now RST2LATEX.
	Create the taf-kit wrappers.
	* doc/makefiles/Makefile.am (docdir): Don't define it, Autoconf 2.60
	takes care of that.
	* doc/Makefile.am (dist_doc_DATA): Don't ship nor install html file.
	Just ship TeX files.
	Use dist_pdf_DATA for PDF files.
	* doc/doc.mk: Use RST2LATEX.
	Don't defined docdir either.
	* doc/manual/Makefile.am: Use pdf_DATA, not doc_DATA.

