2006-07-19  Michal Cadilhac  <michael.cadilhac@lrde.epita.fr>

	TAF: Lessen the use of _CN macros.
	_CN macros of TAF-Kit are used to precise a `Code Name' when it
	differs from the name of the command.  Here, the only difference is
	'_' changed to '-'.  We just print commands changing '_' to '-' now.

	* taf-kit/src/ratexp_commands.hh: Fix typo.
	* taf-kit/src/interface.cc: Change '_' to '-' for command names when
	printing.
	* taf-kit/src/b_commands.cc,
	* taf-kit/src/z_commands.cc: Don't use CN macros.

2006-07-19  Akim Demaille  <akim@lrde.epita.fr>

	More tests.

	* taf-kit/tests/check.mk: Don't override the first line of a log.
	* taf-kit/tests/vcsn-z.test: More tests.

