	The specialization for FMP transducers should come later.


	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/invert.hxx,
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/invert.hh: New. Invert
	  algorithm for rw transducers.

	* include/Makefile.am: Update accordingly.

	* src/tests/automata/algos/boolean_rw_transducers: This
	  directory contains tests for boolean rw transducers
	  exclusively.
	* src/tests/automata/algos/boolean_rw_transducers/invert_test.hh:
	  New. Small test for invert algorithm.
	* src/tests/automata/algos/boolean_rw_transducers/Makefile.am:
	  New.

	* src/tests/test-suites/generate-all.sh,
	* src/tests/automata/algos/Makefile.am: Update accordingly.

	* configure.ac: Update accordingly.

